contest-event.event-date: Aug. 28, 1993 D Edinburgh International Contest Edinburgh International Contest 0 March, Hymn and Own Choice Test Piece Contest edinburgh-international-contest The contest scheduled for 28th August 1993 was cancelled after Edinburgh City Council withdrew financial assistance.
